# Interface ToolCallResultInterface

Result of an executed tool call.

Contains the tool call ID and the result string returned by the executed function. This interface represents the outcome of a tool execution, typically used when the inworld processes tool calls and returns their results.

interface ToolCallResultInterface {  
result: string;  
toolCallId: string;  
}

##### Index

### Properties

result toolCallId

## Properties

### result

result: string

The result string returned by the executed tool/function.

### toolCallId

toolCallId: string

The unique identifier of the tool call that was executed.
